  <front>
   <head>The FLIES.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="octet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">, Sire of Insects, mighty</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">(A Fly upon the Chariot-Pole</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Cries out) what Blew-Bottle alive</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Did ever with such Fury drive?</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Tell, , Great Father, tell</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">(Says t'other, perch'd upon the Wheel)</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Did ever any Mortal Fly</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Raise such a Cloud of Dust, as I?</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="octet">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">My Judgment turn'd the whole Debate:</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">My Valor sav'd the sinking State.</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">So talk two idle buzzing Things;</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Toss up their Heads, and stretch their Wings.</l>
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">But let the Truth to Light be brought:</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">This neither spoke, nor t'other fought:</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">No Merit in their own Behav'or:</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Both rais'd, but by their Party's Favor.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
